# sinabro — .gitignore (deploy-prep, 2026-06-18)
# The distribution repo is the SOURCE needed to build + ship sinabro (the CLI +
# the Tauri desktop app) + the release pipeline. It MUST NOT contain: build
# artifacts (the multi-GB target dirs), the local training corpus / cloned
# third-party sources, or ANY secret / key material. Fail-closed: the patterns
# below are deny-broad; a `git add -n` dry-run audit confirms no secret is staged.

# ── Rust / build artifacts (the multi-GB target dirs — 12GB+ desktop, 5.7GB cli) ──
target/
**/target/
*.rs.bk
*.pdb

# ── Tauri / JS / desktop build ──
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
apps/desktop/cm6-build/node_modules/
apps/desktop/src-tauri/gen/
dist/
.cache/

# ── Local training corpus + cloned third-party sources (NOT the product; 900M+) ──
datasets/
ops/training/domain_corpus/

# ── Secrets / keys / credentials (NEVER committed — defense-in-depth) ──
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*.keystore
memory.key
*.mc
*.minisign
id_ed25519
id_rsa
id_ecdsa
*_rsa
*_ed25519
.env
.env.*
*.secret
*secret*.toml
*credentials*
.netrc
.ssh/

# ── Local data / runtime state (outside the workspace, but excluded defensively) ──
.mnemos/
**/.mnemos/
config.toml.local
*.log

# ── OS / editor junk ──
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/

# ── internal workspace — planning / evidence / tooling (NOT part of the public app) ──
/ops/*
!/ops/release/
/ops/release/*
!/ops/release/install.sh
!/ops/release/install.ps1
!/ops/release/*.md
/atom/
/goal/
/prompt/
/docs/
/tests/
/scripts/
/MNEMOS_*.md
*.prelive_bak
/CLAUDE.md
/.claude/
/.sinabro
/YC_*.md
/prototype/move-prover/
/prototype/docs/
sui-prover.log.*
*.rlib
.sinabro_or_key
